Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.64,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民卫星派来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五部钢弹的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.18,0:01:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是卫星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹躲藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避开联合军机动战士部队的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以OZ为攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开了各种作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.90,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ终于踏上历史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统帅特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以精锐的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行了消灭联合军的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派来地球的机动战士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.25,0:02:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的战斗令大地震动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你当自己的生命是什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆!?别笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样自以为是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前也应该说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人类正确的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四话\N[01爆破指令]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好爱惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏菲亚‧诺边塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在[马赛]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要由那里开始吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来总算赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是陈列用的里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是联合和OZ的主要军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何拘泥于机动战士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的机械会令人害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但同时会有强大的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用双脚走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是不喜欢以按钮分胜负的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们喜欢像人类的战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀人是无分形式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是\N那就是玩弄生命的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战争中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡是更直接的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少人知道OZ带来的混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.67,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实全是罗姆斐拉财团的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团的聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在[雷门]郊外举行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多宾客被邀请参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由欧洲的王侯贵族发起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用庞大财力和人面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直倾全力开发武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她向地球圈统一联合军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提供机动战士，扩张军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令今次政变得以成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法呢，因为我有很多前科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这扇门后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有杀死德利安氏\N和消灭你王国的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为和平主义国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国的后裔\N我不会失礼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去，地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我们寻求很多资金和援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们毫不吝啬\N尽力协助达成和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.35,0:05:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们变得想藉着对话寻求和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地球有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能用对话解决的纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类须要的\N不是受控制的局势吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且\N那以支配的形式得以实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样才能维持和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合无心支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配须要很大的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想逃避责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位拥有能支配时代的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界因为幼小的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这等不完全的思想而堕落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要再次站出来的时刻来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ竟然想以这形式支配世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当他们隐藏在联合之内时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.23,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团没有表露这想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果联合不能为世界带来和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.37,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ就表明它的真正思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不继续胜利\N支配制度就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要胜利后有报酬才成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去的支配制度的崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是对导致贫困的苛政的革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,参加了罗姆斐拉财团的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算继续不败的战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，他们需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最强的机动战士部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是OZ的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹会战胜OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ当钢弹的性能是威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，他们以直接攻击卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令钢弹束手无策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.35,0:07:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团想马上消灭钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想藉很多人的牺牲\N君临世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和希洛为了不产生牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想舍弃生命的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是难以明白的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我介绍率领OZ讨伐联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且为了替世界带来和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们奋勇战斗的骑士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.08,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团的一员兼OZ指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位或许认为OZ会以机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种军事力量作出过份的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配这词语会令人联想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压制及专横的暴政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我认为这是抑制人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过度不必要的欲望的一种统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神抛下人类不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类须要超越神的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无战斗的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越了神的预测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种行为早晚会被神了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧，这里不是我们来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对以为战争是美好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹一定会出现纠正那错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被漂亮话欺骗的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下!请停止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!我还有话要说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里什么也解决不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你，路克蕾琪亚.诺茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，特列斯大人，失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我邀请的朋友的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她刚才想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.75,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她发觉到钢弹令我们不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我们要有多点信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于那部钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杰克斯‧马吉斯也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太纵容区区一个驾驶员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻他在维多利亚基地修复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星派来的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部自爆了的钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然修理\N威胁我们的机动战士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他疯了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为对卫星的警告也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为应该彻底破坏它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很明白你们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是财团的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就叫他马上破坏钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的传闻己经传到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些大人物的耳里了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹凿成OZ的损失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很大的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人看来是反对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能违背上头的决定吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你答应破坏钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很活泼，嫌恶感也很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她知道多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的养父德利安氏临终时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像对她说了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他告诉她你是山克王国出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个可以信赖的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，你是唯一身处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在钢弹01自爆地点的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你在修复钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以她认为那个驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯还生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是那驾驶员的名字吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下和他好像有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，多谢你的报告，诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不向莉莉娜殿下\N表明身份吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报告完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能表明身份!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…重覆着染血历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的杰克斯‧马吉斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，在这所大屋放火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一切烧毁就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，神不会容许那种事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为亵渎神灵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许会受到惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.16,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，一定要作出惩罚吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神是人类想像出来的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈统一联合军的\N诺边塔元帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对作为制衡力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军事扩张抱有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使那是徒然也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他向地球各国及卫星提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裁军甚至全面解除军备的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ把那一日作为新时代的开幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让钢弹击落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔乘坐的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为这是和平的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元…元帅!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别冲动啊，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这事件，世界或许永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法走到通向和平的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏菲亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你快点离开这城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你担心我，上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们地球圈统一联合\N的残余军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集结在马赛这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ袭击我们的行动越来越频繁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以来，因为有联合的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以能守护这城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在基地会带来危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里会成为战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我须要时间抛开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和爷爷在这里生活的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔元帅是个伟大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.91,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直希望有真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷过了身也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷的心愿会留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会好好保存那心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏菲亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉!敌袭!   OZ吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现10部艾亚利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以为那么少军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里就会被攻陷吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心，我们也不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快点去安全的地方，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让艾亚利兹进入居住区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎击开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧各自迎战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直是游击战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.07,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭敌人所有机动战士\N继续攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!我真大意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的里欧后退到地下水道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是主力部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亚利兹全体集合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下水道的里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁也想得出的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管我，现在的我碍手碍脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以给OZ知道钢弹的存在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的部队几乎全军覆没!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至此为止吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在地下水道!别落后!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏菲亚‧诺边塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人艾亚利兹入侵下水道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投降也没用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.47,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会在这种地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亚利兹很快就会来到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!停止后退，迎击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不能拖延很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们要坚持到它的驾驶员回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要保护钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，它是最强的援军!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续!别怕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后…拜托你了…钢弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下水道的里欧全部被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会在这种地方!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在通知其他人前收拾他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在联合和OZ的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我不会有任何感伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N只是钢弹不可以被看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部艾亚利兹被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是奇蹟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部所属不明的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是何方神圣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要感谢他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.01,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你叫希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是爷爷的坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要说的是什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死诺边塔元帅的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我犯了错而击落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔元帅乘坐的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他和很多祈求和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么…为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我只能这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏菲亚‧诺边塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是无可挽救的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深爱元帅的亲人的愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和元帅心有不甘的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你用那支枪令它们息怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想让我这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你自己得到解脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我只能这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太卑鄙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.85,0:19:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你明白我不是来令你难受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.09,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我去见你的婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻她在[西西里亚]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由这里开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有亲人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为自己所犯的错误接受审判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙所做的事好彻底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯所做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争是丑恶的自相残杀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何…把它看成那么漂亮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有这种生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹01爆破完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚哈特调查官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了，我可以收集碎片吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们提出的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什么不满意吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，我想亲眼弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我要做一份令顽固的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.16,0:20:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉大人物认同的报告书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请随便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.24,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么疑点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯也不是一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轻易露出破绽的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,维多利亚基地没有钢弹的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是个喜爱机动战士的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.12,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不会为了我们\N改变自己的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛罗姆斐拉财团\N对他有好处吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯的事我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团开始推动时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要巴结尊贵的资产阶级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯的叛变就要是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个调查官想藉着找寻碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.98,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量搏取罗姆斐拉财团的赏识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎样找也不会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和资料不符的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.66,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你和我一起演戏，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只是觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.33,0:21:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭那部01好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.06,0:21:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，托尔吉斯的后备零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此几乎完全没有了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后不可大意令它受损了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没驾驶员能令杰克斯特校你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和托尔吉斯受损的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.46,0:22:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.71,0:22:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.71,0:22:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.71,0:22:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.21,0:22:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.71,0:23:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.21,0:23:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.71,0:23:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争应该是无情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希洛把自己的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交托给诺边塔夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯想以战士身份决一死战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵邀请希洛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯在等候的南极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚哈特调查官的部队追击他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的再生将要留下新的火种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.02,0:23:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第十五话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.33,0:23:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前往决战地点南极

